## ⚙️ Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn
- Streamlit

---

## 🤖 Machine Learning Model

- Model Used: Random Forest Classifier
- Features Used:
  - Age
  - Monthly Income
  - Years at Company
  - Overtime

- Steps:
  - Data Preprocessing
  - Feature Selection
  - Train-Test Split
  - Model Training
  - Evaluation

---

## 📈 Model Performance

- Evaluated using:
  - Accuracy Score
  - Confusion Matrix
  - Classification Report

---

## 💻 Streamlit Application

An interactive web application was built using Streamlit.

### Features:
- User input form
- Real-time prediction
- Simple and user-friendly UI

